nodes.title: Customize Background Size/自定义背景尺寸

widgets_values:
Set the RGB value to a color similar to the background.
把RGB值设置为跟背景相近的颜色。

Resize the product with the “ImageBlend” node and place it anywhere in the background image.
通过"ImageBlend"节点调整产品的大小，并把它放到背景图的任意位置。

Increasing the brightness will make the image being relighted brighter. Increasing the contrast will make the light in the re-lighted image harder.
增大亮度可以让被重新打光的图像更亮。增大对比度可以让被重新打光的图像的光线更硬。

Set the boolean to True if you want to use the uploaded background image as the final background for the product, or False if you want to use the background image generated by your cue word. Set the boolean to True if you want to repaint the image that was re-lightened, otherwise set it to False. Incorrect Boolean settings may cause the workflow to report an error.
如果你要用上传的背景图作为产品的最终背景，请把布尔值设为True，如果你要用你的提示词生成的背景图，请把布尔值设为False。如果你要对重新打光的图片进行重绘，请把布尔值设为True，否则设为False。布尔值设置不正确可能导致工作流报错。
